OL,4,CHMRC in IT jobs settle pay dispute
OL,6,FStaff working for HM Revenue and
OL,7,FCustoms in IT jobs have settled a pay
OL,8,Fdispute after going on strike, winning
OL,9,Fwage rises of up to 15%, their union
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FMore than 300 members of the Public
OL,13,Fand Commercial Services Union (PCS)
OL,14,Femployed by walked out in January.
OL,16,FThey have voted to accept a deal the
OL,17,Funion said included an extra day of
OL,18,Fannual leave and a promise to review
OL,19,Fout-of-hour rates, as well as higher
OL,20,Fpay.
