OL,4,CHMRC in IT jobs settle pay dispute
OL,6,FPCS general secretary Fran Heathcote
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a fantastic win by our
OL,8,Fmembers at Fujitsu.
OL,10,F"I congratulate them for standing firm
OL,11,Fand winning a pay rise of at least 5%,
OL,12,Fwith the lowest-paid receiving three
OL,13,Ftimes that.
OL,15,F"It's a shame that it took strike
OL,16,Faction for Fujitsu to find the extra
OL,17,Fmoney for our members, but this
OL,18,Fvictory shows what happens when
OL,19,Fworkers stand together. Other private
OL,20,Fsector employers should take note."
